subject: French Open (Tennis)
Laundries and Laundry Aids
Tennis
Fashion and Apparel
lead_paragraph: Up to 4,500 articles of clothing a day at the French Open — tagged by each player’s name — are cleaned at a laundry on the outskirts of Paris.
